## Project 2: Traffic Light Simulator
**Description:** A simulation of a standard three-way traffic light system. This project demonstrates control over multiple GPIO (General Purpose Input/Output) pins simultaneously and implements sequential logic using precise time delays to transition between states safely.

* **Tools Used:** Tinkercad, Arduino C++
* **Hardware Interfaced:** 3x LEDs (Red, Yellow, Green), 3x 220Ω Resistors

